headline: Acadia Pharmaceuticals Set to Join S&P SmallCap 600
summary: Acadia Pharmaceuticals Inc. (NASD: ACAD) will replace Independent Bank Group Inc. (NASD: IBTX) in the S&P SmallCap 600 effective prior to the opening of trading on Friday, January 3, 2025. S&P MidCap 400 constituent SouthState Corp. (NYSE: SSB) is acquiring Independent Bank Group in a deal expected to close soon pending final conditions.
